node.title: Los Angeles Dodgers clinch NL's top seed, 8th straight division title - ESPN
node.description: The Los Angeles Dodgers clinched the National League's top postseason seed and eighth straight division title with a 7-2 victory over the Oakland Athletics on Tuesday.

node.title: Denver Nuggets coach Michael Malone dubs Jamal Murray a superstar after another key performance - ESPN
node.description: "We have two superstars in Nikola and Jamal," Nuggets coach Michael Malone said after Tuesday's win over the Lakers. Jamal Murray had 28 points and 12 assists in the 114-106 win. Nikola Jokic added 22 points and 10 rebounds.
